text: Vicky Kanai is a Palauan politician, who has been a member of the House of Delegates of Palau since 2016. Prior to her election, Kanai served as the Governor of Airai for two terms. ==References== Category:Living people Category:21st-century women politicians Category:Members of the House of Delegates of Palau Category:Palauan women in politics Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
